<p t="32480" d="3900">it&#39;s absurd, I didn&#39;t expect it like that, I think this trip</p>
<p t="36420" d="1860">will be full of surprises</p>
<p t="39240" d="7920">Now we have breakfast and then we leave for the first tour in North Korea</p>
<p t="47160" d="1520">it&#39;s so cold, guys</p>
<p t="63380" d="5300">There is no one in this hotel</p>
